  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Border Community Stabilization along the Northern Land Borders of Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to improve dialogue between border communities and State authorities in northern Ghana by strengthening mutual trust and reinforcing the socio-economic resilience of these communities. Ultimately, through this project, it is expected that border communities and local authorities are engaged in the provision of social amenities to support socio-economic resilience and, border communities are supported with water, sanitation and hygiene facilities that will improve Infection prevention and control capacities to respond to public health emergencies.</narrative>
  </description>
